                        p This settings allows us to use and process information for analytical purposes.
                      label.switch
                        input(type='checkbox')
                        span.slider.round
                    .set
                      .details
                        h5 Data to Customize
                        p This settings allows us to use your information to customize Swipe for you.
                      label.switch
                        input(type='checkbox')
                        span.slider.round
              // End of Privacy & Safety
              // Start of Logout
              .category
                a.title.collapsed(href='sign-in.html')
                  i.material-icons.md-30.online power_settings_new
                  .data
                    h5 Power Off
                    p Log out of your account
                  i.material-icons keyboard_arrow_right
              // End of Logout
